snippet.title: Action 52 - Fire Breathers - 100% Walkthrough
snippet.description: This classic masterpiece has been requested many times, so I figured it was time to give it a shot. This is the first game in a multi game cartridge named Action 52 and it sure lives up to its name. You get 8 levels of hardcore action and the last one is quite challenging with a big obstacle. That's pretty much all there is to say. Enjoy!
